                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" class="rounded-circle me-3" alt="User">
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="mb-0">Michael Brown</h5>
                                <small class="text-muted">IT Administrator</small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text">"The system is intuitive and easy to use. The support team is responsive and helpful whenever we need assistance."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
